This folder contains all the files for the Agamemnon Home Automation Project
GitHub initiated according to: https://www.howtoforge.com/tutorial/install-git-and-github-on-ubuntu-14.04/

Git commands:

1. initialize a new repository
	git init path-to-folder-relative-to-home
2. add a file/folder to the git
	git add add-your-filename-here
3. commit chanes to git
	git commit -m "what was changed"
4. upload local version to GitHub
	git push origin master


